{
	"name": "Legend Dice",
	"type": "feature",
	"img": "icons/sundries/gaming/dice-pair-white-green.webp",
	"system": {
		"description": "<p>At 3rd level, you gain a pool of Legend Dice, which represent your growing mythic momentum. Legend Dice start as a d4 and become a d6 at 10th level and a d10 at 20th level.</p><p>You have a number of Legend Dices equal to your proficiency bonus and you regain all Legend Dices at the end of a long rest.</p><p>You can use a Legend Dice in a few different ways:</p><ul><li><p>When you use a combat maneuver, you may expend a Legend Die to increase its damage by an amount equal to the result of the die or increase its DC by 1.</p></li><li><p>When you are hit by a weapon attack, you may use your reaction to expend a Legend Die and add the result to your AC until the start of your next turn. If this causes the attack to miss, it deals no damage.</p></li><li><p>When you would fall to 0 hit points, you may use your reaction to expend a Legend Die and instead remain at 1 hit point. You can’t use a legend dice this way more than once per short rest.</p></li></ul><p>Additional uses for your Legend Dice become available as you develop your @UUID[Compendium.a5e-fable-of-flames.features.Item.mDrQzw78mvTVZZQR]{Mythic Fable}.</p>",
